~ geonode ~

Bringing geography to node.js.

Example
-------

    var geonode = require("geonode");

    var geom = new geonode.Geometry();
    geom.fromWkt("POINT(1 2)");
    sys.puts(geom.toWkt());

    var geom2 = new geonode.Geometry();
    geom2.fromWkt("POLYGON((0 0, 3 0, 3 3, 0 3, 0 0))");
    sys.puts(geom2.contains(geom)); // "true"

Installation
------------

    $ git clone git://github.com/paulsmith/geonode.git
    $ cd geonode
    $ node-waf configure build

